{"tid":583726,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"法蘭西絲被偷「小金人」 疑犯「奪獎」自拍晒命","createTime":"2018-03-07T08:50:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-07T10:58:01.000Z","uid":160977,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a320373a903f125fdd04b51e321ce32ff271977c","tid":583726,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:50:59.000Z","msg":"第90屆奧斯卡金像獎頒獎禮於昨日圓滿舉行，繼上年大會擺烏龍頒錯獎引全城關注後，今年卻是影后於賽後被偷獎！<br />\n出爐影后法蘭西絲麥杜文（Frances McDormand）憑《廣告牌殺人事件》二度奪獎，心情興奮的她於頒獎禮後的派對上玩得盡興，可惜一時大意，竟被有心之人橫刀「奪獎」！法蘭西絲發現本應握在手上的「小金人」失去影蹤，被指一度激動落淚，與老公四出「尋人」，最後由一位攝影師及保安發現「元兇」。<br />\n<br />\n疑犯是名為Terry Bryant的男人，他偷了法蘭西絲的「小金人」後高調自拍放上網，自稱獲得「最佳製作人獎」，更表示不敢相信自己獲獎，演技逼真。自拍影片期間他獲身邊多位賓客祝賀，他亦有親吻「他的小金人」。在他自拍幾分鐘後他即被捕。事後有網民封疑犯為「最佳演員」，騙到在場的來賓。<br />\n<br />\n法蘭西絲面對失而復得的「小金人」，開心稱其為「小寶貝」，代言人亦發聲明指法蘭西絲已與「小金人」開心重聚，「二人」並一同享受漢堡快餐慶祝。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2IaE8gv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2IaE8gv&d=9DqwGKDBJ0hwxPOAsp97l5UWI6eGpREPWAa3TRi9Bo4%3D&h=52a2a6e9\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2IaE8gv</a>"},{"pid":"707edc08d86fb3a0c0a0012f436bcad96818e747","tid":583726,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:55:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0163qkIGLHVYAQRHSfZoCg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/en-US/homerun/inside_edition/bb19c179691b6b4c7bc027a062772123\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F0163qkIGLHVYAQRHSfZoCg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen-US%2Fhomerun%2Finside_edition%2Fbb19c179691b6b4c7bc027a062772123&h=ba77b55e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0049bec84f6bb11ae5d2815dec7386f86122093c","tid":583726,"uid":121249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T08:56:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13dd5ebe9072a66f329779f82357834b54de00d0","tid":583726,"uid":13